Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as flowing water has no form,\Nand the breeze is invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deductions take all shapes and styles\Nin each and every case to be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Youth Detective Squad\Nare trapped in the cave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's the question\Nof Conan's blood type.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance\Nwith the I.Q. of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No case is left unsolved\Nwith Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, the Youth Detective Squad, went on\Na camping trip with Doctor Agasa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we found a limestone cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We quickly decided to go inside\Nand explore it but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we come across\Nsome men carrying a dead body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and on top of that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get down!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,got shot and suffered a severe injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Footsteps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Those guys are coming!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'll we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:41.57,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,PERILOUS RETURN-\NTHE WOUNDED DETECTIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats! Which one'd they go into?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the kids is hurt,\Nhe won't be moving so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll go after them\Nso you just stand guard here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK! I've got you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did we come in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought these were paths\Nso I picked the farthest one,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how did I know they were just holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we've got to find the dragon's path\Nthat Conan told us about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or we're going to be killed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B, by ourselves, without Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not budging!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he'd create\Na physiological phenomenon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it'd give us\Nthe perfect chance to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't wait for that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, his friends could\Ncome back at anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to get out of this cave\Nas soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we can get Conan to a hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,let's look for the dragon's path\NConan said would lead us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are 5 openings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guard is in front of the rock egg\N...and we're right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this is just a hole &\Ndoesn't go anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the dragon's path must be in\None of the other 4 openings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dragon's path...dragon...dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The word dragon starts with\Nthe letter D doesn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D is the fourth letter in the alphabet!\NX-DISSOLVE WITHIN CUT 1-2-3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the 4th opening\Nis the dragon's path!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 4th from the entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the one we're in right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, Conan was mumbling\Nsomething from behind me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he said\Nthe key words were...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,[to], [dragon], and [egg]\N...something like that....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell us that earlier!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh brother...\Nhe's coming this way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NDidn't I tell you to keep a look out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...did you find them?\NThose kids....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, the 1st opening was a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's 4 more,\Nwe'll find them soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kids might double back here\Nso keep your eyes open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK now, so the key words are\N[to], [dragon] & [egg]...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the dragon were a snake,\Nthen eggs would be their favorite food
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandmother who lives\Nin the country told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was born in the year of\Nthe snake so she studied them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Year of the snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,[To], [dragon], and [egg] pertain\Nto the Chinese zodiac.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dragon means year of the dragon,\Negg means year of the snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but what about [to]?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably means year of\Nthe tiger (tora) or chicken (tori)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we put the egg into\Nthe snake's position,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the 5 openings and their pertaining\Nzodiac symbols will be like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,year of the dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which is the dragon's path,\Nis right next to the egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't that the opening\Nthose killers said was a dead end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides, I think year of the chicken\Nis better suited for the word egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B, but...then the meaning will\Noverlap with the word [to].
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, maybe\Nit's pointing to the year of the rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The character for rabbit looks\Na lot like the character for egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's the chicken that lays eggs....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...I think [to], [dragon], and [egg]\Naren't referring to the zodiac after all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:07:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the only other common denominator\Nis they're all written in 1 character...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about!\NEgg is 2 characters, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to a restaurant close to where I live\Nand I read [tamago yaki] as [ohji yaki]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And everybody, even mom laughed at\Nme, that's why I'll never forget the word!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And tamago is sometimes\Nwritten as tama no ko too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, just wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, it could be,\Nit just could be, that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it has something\Nto do with "shogi" (chess)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,[To] is in back of the pawn and\N[dragon] is in back of the rook
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just like Genta said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the character for egg could be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the one he mentioned\Nwhich would stand for "gyokusho"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's gyokusho?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In chess, it's the king the player\Nwith the lower score uses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is, if the egg is\Nreferring to the position of the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the 5 openings would be ranked\Naccording to their proximity to the egg
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,thus they would be\N[kinsho], [ginsho], [keima], [kosha],
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the opening in front of the [keima]\Nwould be the path of the rook and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the dragon's path?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opening diagonally\Nin front of it is the way out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't get to that one\Nwithout passing in front of that man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only weapons,\Nif you can call them that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we have is our watch shaped\Nflashlights and our badges...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our badges?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember right, Conan....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen! I don't know if it'll work but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can\Nknock me out with those rocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now! Let's go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's those kids!\NThey went into that opening...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll teach them!\NThey won't get away from me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the exit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ge, Genta!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha, I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK you two!\NDon't step outside, get back in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry it up!\NI'll shoot him in the head if you don't!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, good kiddies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're completely surrounded!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw down your guns and\Ncome out with your hands up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I repeat!\NYou are completely surrounded!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fools! Don't you see what I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't me to shoot this kid,\Nyou'd better let me through!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already read your next move...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Play it smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how the 3 robbers were caught\Nand our cave exploration came to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Doctor Agasa and Haibara\Nthat notified the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They figured we'd be\Nheading for the cave's exit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so they talked to the local people\Nand found out about this exit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they'd just arrived to stake it out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to this local man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that mysterious sign\Nhas been around for ages
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no one knows for sure who wrote it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My consciousness started to slip\Nas I listened to the conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was taken to\Nthe Beika General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Surgery???
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it just a scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...uh..er..you see...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bullet passed through\Nthe abdomen on the left side
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there was a lot of bleeding and\Nthere's a possibility of kidney damage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's in a very serious condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, hang in there!\NYou'll be fine in a little while!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doctor, we have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The previous patient we operated on\Nhas this boy's blood type
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we used up almost\Nall the blood we had in stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if we call the blood bank now,\Nwe'll never get it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can use my blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He and I have the same blood type!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you'd better check to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry then, let's get you tested
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran....I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you did know after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like I'm still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:13:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch....boy this pain doesn't give up...\Nand neither do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You owe her your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She gave you 400 cc\Nof her own blood and on top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she stayed up all night watching you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lucky you and Ran just happened\Nto have the same blood type
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had a rare blood type,\Nyou wouldn't be here today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd be in the next world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...you can use my blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He and I have the same blood type!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't a guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran knew for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knew my blood type...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knows who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran gave you a whole lot of her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd get better fast\Nor I'm going to get you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yessir!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:14:00.59,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,10 Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! There was no damage to any\Nmajor organ and he's healing very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at this rate, he'll be able to check out\Nin 2 or 3 days, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One thing though....after the operation,\Nhis resistance is low
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it appears he has an infection\Nin his upper respiratory tract...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An upper respiratory tract infection?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's just a cold
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See! Didn't I tell you this game's neat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really popular at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go left there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Play time is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw shucks!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The patient is to return\Nstraight to his room!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for you kids,\Nit's getting late so go on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw gee
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll see you at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said you could leave in 2 or 3 days,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,our school's having\Nthe school festival then
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3 days from today,\Nthat's the day we have our play
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't pick him up...\Nyou'll be busy all morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'll ask dad to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you\Nget a hold of "you know who"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he finds out you're playing the lead,\NI'm sure he'll come flying
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't come...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...\Nit doesn't matter to me anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy just having Conan get better\Nand coming to see the play...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh???
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will come, won't you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this???\NYou two're acting so lovey-dovey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, don't tell me you're switching\Nfrom Shinichi to this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! That's ridiculous!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, what happened to your wrist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sprained it during rehearsal,\Nthat's why I can't play the knight's part...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're lucky someone that nice\Noffered to take your place
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:15:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, Mr. Arade,\Nthe teacher I told you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit but\Nhe's awfully good at it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that love scene\Nwith Ran is something!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heh...I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if Ran can keep a cool head in front\Nof all those people, the play'll be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cooler in the gym is broken\Nand it'll be like a sauna inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,besides, there wasn't\Nmuch of a crowd last year either...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet that scrawny guy\Nplanned things to work out this way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know,\Nthings will be different this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drama club is putting up a stand in\Nthe gym, they're going to sell cold drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I don't believe it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world were you thinking of?!\NWhy'd you go and buy lilies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers are flowers,\Nwhat's the difference?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't those voices\Ncoming from your room, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That voice, it couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dope! Lilies have a strong smell,\Nsome people don't like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't buy them\Nfor people in the hospital!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me that before!\NYou ninny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji, Kazuha, I didn't expect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo! I heard the kid got hurt bad so we\Nhopped on a plane after school got out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine! He's healing very well, they said\Nhe'll be able to leave in 2 or 3 days!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind that! I brought you\Nsome great flowers to send you off with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?\NYou have some nerve!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you girls go with Kazuha\Nso she doesn't get lost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why of course
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?\NSo what's the real reason you came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hurt my feelings, I came all this way\Njust to see how you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was shot in the stomach too,\Nwe've got things in common
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is so important you had to come\Nall this way and with flowers even
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heh, I guess I can't fool you, huh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truth is, I got a call from an old guy\Nnamed Agasa, last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to talk to me about you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on but, Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that girlie's starting to\Nget suspicious about who you really are!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No she's not suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She already knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're kidding, you told her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you and that old man\Ncould be wrong about the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so scared she'll find out,\Nyour imagination got the best of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's been a lot of signs she knows
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And unless I can come up with\Nanother me, I don't think I can fool her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if she knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why doesn't she just tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed,\Nyou can read other people's minds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you don't have the slightest idea\Nwhat's going on with yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that girl knows and she's not saying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then there's only 1 reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's waiting!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants to hear it from you personally!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you have to prepare\Nfor the worst and tell her everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,about the so called group of men in black
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and about the potion that\Nmade you shrink, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you expect me to tell her\Nall that? She's a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She listens to everyone's problems,\Nworries for them, and cries for them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can I do that to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can keep lying to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not after seeing how strained she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really want to tell her everything\Nand get it off my chest but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Heiji!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the last day of the school fest,\Nyou know the play Ran's in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's on a Sunday,\Nso you'll come with me won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless I can come up with another me,\NI don't think I can fool her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry but I can't go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have something to do that day.\NI can't get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's important...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen Shinichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must never tell anyone about this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that includes Ran!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that girl knows but isn't saying anything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there's only 1 reason why!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't let anyone know about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants you to tell her personally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I've got to tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,На...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.71,0:24:27.65,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,PERILOUS RETURN-\NSHINICHI IS BACK
